# Example usage

## Visualize

```shell
opctl ui {{opYml.name}}#{{opYml.version}}
```

## Run

```
opctl run {{opYml.name}}#{{opYml.version}}
```

## Compose

```yaml
op:
  ref: {{opYml.name}}#{{opYml.version}}
  {{#if opYml.inputs}}
  {{#ifAnyRequiredInputs opYml.inputs}}
  inputs:
  {{#each opYml.inputs}}
  {{#ifOpInputRequired this}}
    {{@key}}:  # ðŸ‘ˆ required; provide a value
  {{/ifOpInputRequired}}
  {{/each}}
  {{/ifAnyRequiredInputs}}
  {{#ifAnyOptionalInputs opYml.inputs}}
  ## uncomment to override defaults
  {{#ifNoRequiredInputs opYml.inputs}}
  # inputs:
  {{/ifNoRequiredInputs}}
  {{#each opYml.inputs}}
  {{#ifOpInputOptional this}}
  #   {{@key}}: {{{opInputDefault this}}}
  {{/ifOpInputOptional}}
  {{/each}}
  {{/ifAnyOptionalInputs}}
  {{/if}}
  {{#if opYml.outputs}}
  outputs:
  {{#each opYml.outputs}}
    {{@key}}:
  {{/each}}
  {{/if}}
```

